  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.4.3">
<l>vaiyaṇainta nutikkōṭṭu varāka moṉṟāy maṇṇellā miṭanteṭuttu mataṅkaḷ ceytu</l>
<l>neyyaṇainta tikiriyiṉāl vāṇaṉ tiṇṭōḷ nērntavaṉṟā ḷaṇaikiṟpīr neyta lōṭu</l>
<l>maiyaṇainta kuvaḷaikaḷtaṅ kaṇka ḷeṉṟum malarkkumutam vāyeṉṟum kaṭaici mārkaḷ</l>
<l>ceyyaṇaintu kaḷaikaḷaiyā tēṟuṅ kāḻic cīrāma viṇṇakarē cērmi ṉīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would touch the feet of the one who attacked</l>
<l rend="indent">the strong arms of Vāṇa with a discus touched with blood,</l>
<l>Having dug and taken up the entire world, causing high spirits,</l>
<l rend="indent">as a boar with tusks whose tips were touched with sharpness,</l>
<l>Gather you [all] at Cīrāmaviṇṇakaram in Kāḻi where peasant women,</l>
<l rend="indent">having gone to the [paddy] field,</l>
<l>Thinking dark lilies and lilies touched with black [marks] are eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">and thinking blooming red lilies are lips,</l>
<l rend="indent">clamber [out] without weeding [those] weeds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
